<div class="article__photo-meta">
<span data-img-caption="Traveling across the West, Jeffrey Dean Caldwell presented himself as a free-spirited outdoor archetype for over a decade. " class="article__caption">Traveling across the West, Jeffrey Dean Caldwell presented himself as a free-spirited outdoor archetype for over a decade. </span>
